sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as EndUser
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant AuthMW as GatewayAuthMiddleware
participant PermMW as GatewayPermissionMiddleware
participant AuthSvc as AuthService
participant UserAuthDb as MongoUserAuth
participant Redis as RedisRefreshStore
participant UserSvc as UserServiceBootstrap
Note over User,Client: Luong 1 - Dang ky va kich hoat
User->>Client: Nhap form dang ky
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/register
Gateway->>AuthMW: Verify request format/public route
AuthMW-->>Gateway: pass
Gateway->>PermMW: Bypass permission (public auth route)
PermMW-->>Gateway: pass
Gateway->>AuthSvc: Forward register payload
AuthSvc->>UserAuthDb: Validate + tao UserAuth (inactive, unverified)
alt Du lieu hop le
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 201 + verify instruction
  Gateway-->>Client: Register success
else Email trung/Password yeu/DOB sai
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 400/409
  Gateway-->>Client: Hien thi loi nghiep vu
end
Note over User,UserSvc: Luong 2 - Verify email
User->>Client: Mo link verify
Client->>Gateway: GET /api/auth/verify-email?token=...
Gateway->>AuthSvc: Forward verify token
AuthSvc->>UserAuthDb: Check token + set isActive/isEmailVerified
alt Token hop le
  AuthSvc->>UserSvc: Internal bootstrap profile
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 200 verified
  Gateway-->>Client: Tai khoan san sang dang nhap
else Token het han/sai
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 400/410
  Gateway-->>Client: Verify that bai
end
Note over User,Redis: Luong 3 - Dang nhap va refresh
User->>Client: Dang nhap
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/login
Gateway->>AuthSvc: Forward login
AuthSvc->>UserAuthDb: Check password + lock state
alt Login hop le
  AuthSvc->>Redis: SET refresh_token:<userId>
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 200 access+refresh
  Gateway-->>Client: Tra token
else Chua verify/bi lock/sai mat khau
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 401/423
  Gateway-->>Client: Tu choi dang nhap
end
